OL,3,CMan who stalked radio DJ avoids prison
OL,5,FA stalker who left a radio DJ feeling
OL,6,F"unsafe and paranoid" by repeatedly
OL,7,Fsending her letters, emails and gifts
OL,8,Fhas been spared jail.
OL,10,FKeaton Adams, of Englefield Green,
OL,11,FSurrey, even turned up at the Heart
OL,12,Fradio studio in Leicester Square in
OL,13,Fcentral London in January this year,
OL,14,Fasking to see presenter Katrina Ridley.
OL,16,FThe 51-year-old persistently tried to
OL,17,Fcontact Ms Ridley between November 1
OL,18,F2024 and February 20 2025 because he
OL,19,Fbelieved he was in a relationship with
OL,20,Fher, Westminster Magistrates' Court
OL,21,Fheard on Tuesday.
