OL,3,CMan who stalked radio DJ avoids prison
OL,5,FIn December, 60 messages, some of
OL,6,Fwhich were "delusional in nature",
OL,7,Fwere sent in just three hours,
OL,8,Fprosecutors said.
OL,10,FOne message sent to the radio station
OL,11,Fread: "I'm going to say goodnight now
OL,12,Fbaby girl... I love you always."
OL,14,FAdams contacted Ms Ridley on her
OL,15,Fpersonal email, wrote about her having
OL,16,F"spyware" at his home and said they
OL,17,Fwere going to get married in
OL,18,FAustralia, the court heard.
