OL,3,CMan who stalked radio DJ avoids prison
OL,5,FIn December 2024, he sent coffee mugs
OL,6,Fto the studio with "I will always love
OL,7,Fyou" printed on them.
OL,9,FMs Ridley said in her victim impact
OL,10,Fstatement that the stalking had "a
OL,11,Fhuge impact" on her life, leaving her
OL,12,Ffeeling "unsafe and paranoid" and
OL,13,Funable to use public transport.
OL,15,FAdams had pleaded guilty to one count
OL,16,Fof stalking involving serious alarm or
OL,17,Fdistress.
OL,19,FHe was jailed for 16 weeks, suspended
OL,20,Ffor 18 months.
